a\equiv b\pmod m
c+d\equiv 0\pmod m
ac+bd\equiv 0\pmod m
a\equiv b\pmod m\Longrightarrow m\mid a-b\Longrightarrow m\mid c(a-b)\Longrightarrow m\mid ac-bc\Longrightarrow \\ac-bc=mk
c+d\equiv 0\pmod m\Longrightarrow m\mid c+d\Longrightarrow m\mid b(c+d)\Longrightarrow m\mid bc+bd\\bc+bd=mj
ac-bc+bc+bd=mk+mj\\ac+bd=m(k+j)\\m\mid ac+bd\Longrightarrow ac+bd\equiv0\pmod m\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\Box
